		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<P>Nice writeup Xalmat.</P>
<P>I'd like to accentuate&nbsp;a premise that comes from our class description:&nbsp; Elemental pets are the heart of our offensive strategy, the pet is supposed to provide protection for the magician,&nbsp;and Magician's are able to adventure solo. Currently, I feel that the magician class suffers because SOE hasn't stuck with this definition very well at all.</P>
<DIV>Otherwise, I find the writeup very thoughtful. It does something that gets glossed over in a lot of balancing discussions, it actually provides some balancing tweaks for all levels within the class.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
